imilarities between\nhateful/normal users and their 1-neighborhood, suggesting strong homophily.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 31 Dec 2017 17:08:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 14 Jan 2018 15:21:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-16"}
