se of the Gaussian network, we further establish that\nunder individual fronthaul constraints, the compression strategy achieves to\nwithin a constant gap to the \\emph{sum} capacity of the C-RAN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jan 2018 04:57:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jul 2019 12:53:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-23"}
